  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 5)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This package re-evaluates COU1 at Model Risk Level 5 following a regulatory request to treat the decision consequence as Critical and model influence as High. Several credibility factors remain not-assessed despite the elevated risk level, which materially weakens the overall credibility of the submission.",
